---
title: Tunisian-Style Chickpea Stew with Harissa Chili Oil & Za'atar-Spiced Pitas
description: This hearty vegetarian Tunisian-style stew is layered with fragrant spices in every bite. You’ll simmer chickpeas with onion, tomatoes, cumin, paprika, and garlic until rich and thick. Garnish your bowls with a dollop of yogurt, fresh cilantro, and a drizzle of harissa oil made with the fiery North African spice. Warm toasted za'atar-spiced pitas make for the perfect accompaniment.
